ersal relation largely deviates from that\nof general relativity, allowing, in principle, to probe the existence of\nspontaneous scalarization with future observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2016 16:25:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Jun 2016 11:56:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-22"}
