as to\ncosmological parameters determined from the lensing power spectrum,\nspecifically w, {\\Omega}m and {\\sigma}8.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2016 19:03:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-08"}
