extensive set of approximate and exact\ncomparators. An empirical illustration completes the paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Apr 2016 06:55:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Jan 2017 05:46:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 2 Dec 2018 22:53:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-04"}
