rms state-of-the-art context-based schemes consistently for\nboth small and large training datasets. For lossy contour coding, our\nalgorithms outperform comparable schemes in the literature in rate-distortion\nperformance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Apr 2016 10:00:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-21"}
