nslope and normalization. These results provide a benchmark to compare with data\nfrom the 2015 outburst of V404 Cyg and, potentially, other transient LMXBs as\nwell.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Apr 2016 11:37:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-03"}
