gular blocked tensor (all of whose\ndiagonal blocks are irreducible). We give an example to show that this is not\ntrue for the first type canonical upper triangular blocked tensor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Apr 2016 11:51:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-29"}
